&amp;pages=027002&amp;doi=10.1117%2F1.JMI.3.2.027002&amp;pmid=27158633">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">9.</div><div id="r9" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">D’Orsi CJ, Sickles EA, Mendelson EB, Morris EA. ACR BI-RADS ultrasound, coronal and axial diagrams of breast anatomy. 5th ed. Reston, Va: American College of Radiology, 2013; 13.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=ACR+BI-RADS+ultrasound%2C+coronal+and+axial+diagrams+of+breast+anatomy&amp;author=CJ+D%E2%80%99Orsi&amp;author=EA+Sickles&amp;author=EB+Mendelson&amp;author=EA+Morris&amp;publication_year=2013">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">10.</div><div id="r10" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Giger ML, Inciardi MF, Edwards A, et al. Automated breast ultrasound in breast cancer screening of women with dense breasts: reader study of mammography-negative and mammography-positive cancers. <em>AJR Am J Roentgenol</em> 2016;206(6):1341–1350.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.2214/AJR.15.15367">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/27043979/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Automated+breast+ultrasound+in+breast+cancer+screening+of+women+with+dense+breasts%3A+reader+study+of+mammography-negative+and+mammography-positive+cancers&amp;author=ML+Giger&amp;author=MF+Inciardi&amp;author=A+Edwards&amp;publication_year=2016&amp;journal=AJR+Am+J+Roentgenol&amp;pages=1341-1350&amp;doi=10.2214%2FAJR.15.15367&amp;pmid=27043979">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">11.</